Text: Updated NETCO TestingPST Hi Please see the attached document with the correct date that corresponds with the meeting request In addition the Canadian and Portland users are also included The Bridgeline CODE will be open during this time for us discuss and resolve issues Thanks Hi Attached is schedule for NETCO testing for Friday afternoon The objectives for tomorrow will be to Test logins for NETCO users and drive mappings Execute a subset of the Gas and Power scenarios to test that all platform components are setup The complete set of scenarios will be tested next week We appreciate your support as we work towards setting up the NETCO platform which has a number of moving parts that are coming together Thanks Aftab

Front Office NETCO TestingPST Hi Let us plan to meet to perform preliminary integration testing for the Front Office for NETCO We are working on completing the front office application migration by early afternoon The objectives for this meeting will be Validate front office deal entry scenarios for EOL Sitara EnPower TDS and TAGGERMS Execute sample scenarios Review the integration testing effort for tomorrow with connectivity to the back office applications Please let us know if you have any questions Thanks Aftab
